  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe and Oceania. The aim of this trial is to assess the effect
      on glycemic control of NNC 90-1170 (liraglutide) added to metformin compared to metformin
      given alone in subjects with type 2 diabetes previously treated with OHAs (oral hypoglycaemic
      agents).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
